A preview of “Grey’s Anatomy” favorite Dr. Miranda Bailey having an apparent heart attack in next week’s episode caused fans’ hearts to stop Thursday. The title of the episode, “(Don’t Fear) The Reaper,” only made it worse. Viewers threatened to stop watching the show if Bailey, played by Chandra Wilson for 14 seasons, dies. The promo aired after Thursday’s broadcast of the medical drama on ABC and spread like an epidemic on social media. The response was pretty much a code blue of anger. what the fuck. WHAT THE ACTUAL FUCK! Y’all better not take Dr.Miranda Bailey from us, i swear to gosh.... https://t.co/dvprdKqZbH I SWEAR TO GOD IF THEY KILL DR BAILEY IM DONE stg that if Shonda Rhimes takes Dr. Miranda Bailey, I’m done. I will quit watching the show for good. You’ve taken almost everyone else away from me, you are NOT taking her. Me: Man today’s a great dayGrey’s Anatomy: Lol we might kill Miranda Bailey Me: pic.twitter.com/dXJh5Ioo9Q @shondarhimes YOU HAVE GONE TOO FAR. IF YOU TAKE DR. BAILEY I WILL NEVER FORGIVE YOU. #GreysAnatomypic.twitter.com/M0nI3zexyN On GOD if Dr.Bailey dies I am not watching Grey's anymore ever again So why do fans love Dr. Bailey so much? Watch this clip from Thursday’s episode as she gives her son THE TALK about how to behave if he’s stopped by the cops.